                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-135-18411129 t18411129-135-punishment-120"></join>Transported for Ten Years</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">DAVIS—
<rs id="t18411129-135-verdict-1" type="verdictDescription">
